{"tid":1783412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地真係好痴線！","createTime":"2019-12-14T18:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T20:09:36.000Z","uid":266286,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e33e2717dc0901d510f22736d65e616d3380f7a9","tid":1783412,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:44:29.000Z","msg":"我們一眾在德港人於德國出席國會聽證會商討德版《人權法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1783307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1783307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我明架<br />\n日日百鳩幾份野要簽<br />\n而且大部分簽完都無回音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係今次！</span><br />\n連黃之鋒都開到聲叫我地簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明依份野真係重要重要重要<br />\n你唔係嚴麻煩唔簽吓話？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要夠target 人地先做到野</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n岩岩我簽完先發覺原來真係唔洗識德文都簽到<br />\n禁完枝筆之後 禁右上角註冊帳號<br />\n有星既長方形是但打啲野填左去<br />\n有星既格仔就是但剔左佢<br />\n之後驗證email<br />\n根本上同其他地方既註冊方式一模一樣<br />\n所以根本唔存在語言既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個過程2分鐘都唔洗<br />\n<br />\n真係好痴線啊！！！～"},{"pid":"8a9b08db926013ff7b1f1d1c8606c9d50ea3f382","tid":1783412,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:44:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推，今日既行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNdDXFS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNdDXFS.jpg&h=15fcca53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Mc9jUc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Mc9jUc.jpg&h=5084b6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNY1a0T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNY1a0T.jpg&h=f557520a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"184a12bbc3a24acb140290934cd7b3901b246c9c","tid":1783412,"uid":263366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":